    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts RHI within 12% of bench measurements across all operating points. RHI < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied. A screening sensitivity study on blood rheological parameters confirmed that nominal input choices yield conservative hemolysis predictions. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
